Package org.gradoop.flink.model.impl.operators.aggregation.functions

aggregate functions

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AggregateEdges
    Applies edge aggregate functions to the edges.
    AggregateTransactions
    Applies an AggregateFunction to the vertex or edge set of a graph transaction.
    AggregateVertices
    Applies vertex aggregate functions to the vertices.
    ApplyAggregateEdges
    Applies edge aggregate functions to edges with the same graph id.
    ApplyAggregateVertices
    Applies vertex aggregate functions to vertices with the same graph id.
    CombinePartitionAggregates
    Aggregates the aggregate values of different partitions
    CombinePartitionApplyAggregates
    Aggregates the aggregate values of partitions with the same graph id
    GetPropertyValue<EL extends Element>
    Extracts a PropertyValue from a given entity using a given property key.
    GraphIdsWithPropertyValue<GE extends GraphElement>
    Takes a graph element and a property key as input and builds one tuple of graph id and property value per graph the vertex is contained in.
    GroupCountToPropertyValue
    Wraps the result of a group-by-id-count into a property value
    SetAggregateProperties
    Sets aggregate values of a graph heads.
    SetAggregateProperty
    Sets aggregate values of a graph head.
